    {
      "text": "Micro Machines are a line of toys originally made by Galoob (now part of Hasbro) from 1987 and throughout the 1990s. Micro Machines are tiny scale component style \"playsets\" and vehicles that are slightly larger than N scale.",
      "lang": "en",
